description: Demolition of 1-40 Ethelbert Close, 2 Ethelbert Road, 102-108 High Street and miscellaneous buildings to the north of Ethelbert Close (including former public conveniences and building at rear of 100 High Street), and the redevelopment of the site (max height 16 levels) to provide a mixed use scheme comprising 407 residential units with a mix of Use Class A1, A2, A3, B1, D1, D2 uses at ground floor (part). New vehicular access from Ethelbert Road. Associated basement car and cycle parking. Car parking, access and servicing arrangements at Churchill Way.  Public realm works including Library Gardens and ancillary development.
